<p>10 tade legei kurioV kurioV kai apolw plhqoV Aiguptiwn dia ceiroV Naboucodonosor basilewV BabulwnoV</p>
<p>11 autou kai tou laou autou loimoi apo eqnwn apestalmenoi apolesai thn ghn kai ekkenwsousin panteV taV macairaV autwn ep Aigupton kai plhsqhsetai h gh traumatiwn</p>
<p>12 kai dwsw touV potamouV autwn erhmouV kai apolw thn ghn kai to plhrwma authV en cersin allotriwn egw kurioV lelalhka</p>
<p>13 oti tade legei kurioV kurioV kai apolw megistanaV apo MemfewV kai arcontaV ek ghV Aiguptou kai ouk esontai eti</p>
