<p>15 otan dw Aigupton eiV apwleian kai erhmwqh h gh sun th plhrwsei authV otan diaspeirw pantaV touV katoikountaV en auth kai gnwsontai oti egw eimi kurioV</p>
<p>16 qrhnoV estin kai qrhnhseiV auton kai ai qugatereV twn eqnwn qrhnhsousin auton ep Aigupton kai epi pasan thn iscun authV qrhnhsousin authn legei kurioV kurioV</p>
<p>17 kai egenhqh en tw dwdekatw etei tou prwtou mhnoV pentekaidekath tou mhnoV egeneto logoV kuriou proV me legwn</p>
<p>18 uie anqrwpou qrhnhson epi thn iscun Aiguptou kai katabibasousin authV taV qugateraV ta eqnh nekraV eiV to baqoV thV ghV proV touV katabainontaV eiV boqron</p>
<p>19 </p>
